@page
@model IndexModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Начало";
}

<section class="home-hero">
    <div class="home-hero__content">
        <h1 class="home-hero__title">
            Открий билките около теб
        </h1>

        <p class="home-hero__subtitle">
            BilkoNavigator е платформа за откриване, разпознаване и споделяне
            на лечебни билки в България – директно върху интерактивна карта.
        </p>

        <div class="home-hero__actions">
            <a asp-controller="Map" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-primary-custom">
                <svg class="home-hero__btn-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                    <path d="M9 4L3 6.5V20L9 17.5L15 20L21 17.5V4L15 6.5L9 4Z" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                    <path d="M9 4V17.5M15 6.5V20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" />
                </svg>
                <span>Отвори картата</span>
            </a>

            <a asp-controller="Recognition" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-secondary-custom">
                <svg class="home-hero__btn-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                    <path d="M12 20C12 15 14 10 20 6C20 12 17 18 12 20Z" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                    <path d="M12 20C12 14 9 10 4 8C4 14 7 18 12 20Z" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                    <path d="M12 20V10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" />
                </svg>
                <span>Разпознай билка</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="home-hero__visual" aria-hidden="true">
        <img src="~/images/hero-gnome.png"
             asp-append-version="true"
             alt=""
             class="home-hero__visual-img" />
    </div>
</section>

<section class="home-features">
    <div class="home-features__inner">
        <div class="home-features__heading">
            <p class="home-features__eyebrow">С BilkoNavigator</p>
            <h2 class="home-section-title">Какво можеш да правиш</h2>
            <p class="home-features__lead">
                Избери действие и започни веднага. Всичко е организирано така, че
                да стигнеш до най-важното с 1-2 клика.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="home-features__grid">
            <article class="feature-card feature-card--map">
                <div class="feature-card__top">
                    <span class="feature-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path d="M9 4L3 6.5V20L9 17.5L15 20L21 17.5V4L15 6.5L9 4Z" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                            <path d="M9 4V17.5M15 6.5V20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" />
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span class="feature-card__tag">Карта</span>
                </div>
                <h3>Карта на билките</h3>
                <p>
                    Виж къде в България растат различни билки и кои са най-близо до теб.
                </p>
                <a asp-controller="Map" asp-action="Index" class="feature-card__link">Отвори картата</a>
            </article>

            <article class="feature-card feature-card--recognition">
                <div class="feature-card__top">
                    <span class="feature-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <rect x="3" y="7" width="18" height="13" rx="2.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" />
                            <path d="M9 7L10.5 4.8H13.5L15 7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                            <circle cx="12" cy="13.5" r="3.2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" />
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span class="feature-card__tag">Модел</span>
                </div>
                <h3>Разпознаване</h3>
                <p>
                    Качи снимка и получи информация за вида, свойствата и употребата.
                </p>
                <a asp-controller="Recognition" asp-action="Index" class="feature-card__link">Разпознай билка</a>
            </article>

            <article class="feature-card feature-card--catalog">
                <div class="feature-card__top">
                    <span class="feature-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path d="M4 6.5C4 5.1 5.1 4 6.5 4H18V18H6.5C5.1 18 4 19.1 4 20.5V6.5Z" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                            <path d="M18 18H6.8C5.3 18 4 19.2 4 20.7H18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                            <path d="M8 8H14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" />
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span class="feature-card__tag">Библиотека</span>
                </div>
                <h3>Каталог</h3>
                <p>
                    Разгледай пълен списък с билки, описания и полезни съвети.
                </p>
                <a asp-controller="Herbs" asp-action="Index" class="feature-card__link">Виж каталога</a>
            </article>

            <article class="feature-card feature-card--contribute">
                <div class="feature-card__top">
                    <span class="feature-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path d="M12 21C12 21 18 15.2 18 10.2C18 6.8 15.3 4 12 4C8.7 4 6 6.8 6 10.2C6 15.2 12 21 12 21Z" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                            <circle cx="12" cy="10.2" r="2.3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" />
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span class="feature-card__tag">Общност</span>
                </div>
                <h3>Добавяне на билки</h3>
                <p>
                    Сподели открити от теб билки и помогни на общността.
                </p>
                <a asp-controller="Herbs" asp-action="Create" class="feature-card__link">Добави билка</a>
            </article>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="home-about">
    <h2 class="home-section-title">Защо BilkoNavigator?</h2>
    <p class="home-about__text">
        Проектът цели да съхрани и популяризира знанията за лечебните растения,
        като ги направи достъпни чрез модерни уеб технологии и интерактивна карта.
    </p>
</section>
